{"tid":1394231,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"更衣室為巴爾取名「高爾夫選手」","createTime":"2019-08-01T10:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T10:12:19.000Z","uid":1426,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"41e017c62f3cd938002ffacedd91703dce687da4","tid":1394231,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:48:37.000Z","msg":"在奧迪杯0-1不敵熱刺之後，皇馬教練施丹（Z.Zidane）曾在賽後記者會對巴爾（G.Bale）沒有隨隊出征進行瞭解釋，「我們決定不帶巴爾是因為他感覺不舒服，我和醫生以及球員談過了，我們認為最好是讓他留在馬德里訓練。」<br />\n<br />\n　　而據西班牙媒體《機密報》報導，在奧迪杯進行期間，巴爾在馬德里附近打高爾夫球，<span style=\"color: red;\">高圖爾斯（T.Courtois）則透露巴爾在皇馬更衣室內部被稱作「高爾夫選手」。</span><br />\n<br />\n　　關於巴爾的未來仍然懸而未決，此前曾有消息稱巴爾將加盟江蘇蘇寧，但現在看來這筆轉會已經不可能實現，英超也有可能是巴爾的去處，但目前沒有球隊願意負擔巴爾的1700萬歐元年薪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hxTMQLF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhxTMQLF.png&h=d47361a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f8ecb54175ed6a681a2a5e1301f56f9c1e8a5de","tid":1394231,"uid":79562,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zvDAy5L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzvDAy5L.png&h=3e01c08c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fccaa66eb6085fc2ee7826de0e7c85a116f50a6","tid":1394231,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3f8ecb54175ed6a681a2a5e1301f56f9c1e8a5de","tid":1394231,"uid":79562,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zvDAy5L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzvDAy5L.png&h=3e01c08c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />46"},{"pid":"ea08e4227db5f5fd6dc798ee4224f87d51dfef5f","tid":1394231,"uid":127362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:35:25.000Z","